WEBVTT

00:51.919 --> 00:54.823
<i>You never forget your first love.</i>

00:54.888 --> 00:56.825
<i>You carry it with you always.</i>

00:56.890 --> 01:01.196
<i>The right song instantly
takes you back to that time.</i>

01:01.261 --> 01:03.764
<i>For me, it was the summer of '63.</i>

01:03.831 --> 01:06.468
<i>Jackie Kennedy was still queen of Camelot</i>

01:06.533 --> 01:09.705
<i>and I was still known to my family as "Baby."</i>

01:09.770 --> 01:12.341
<i>The Feminine Mystique.</i> What does that mean?

01:12.406 --> 01:15.711
It's about how women's magazines
portray housewives as happy

01:15.776 --> 01:19.481
and career girls as unhappy,
when it's usually the opposite.

01:19.546 --> 01:21.450
I have to throw out my magazines?

01:21.515 --> 01:23.352
<i>My older sister Lisa,</i>

01:23.417 --> 01:26.355
<i>a college girl majoring in finding a husband.</i>

01:26.420 --> 01:30.492
