of Marriage," is that their agenda?

01:30.557 --> 01:34.196
All those articles are about sex
and beauty and fashion,

01:34.261 --> 01:36.398
- as if that's all women care about.
- Girls, please,

01:36.463 --> 01:39.134
your father hasn't taken a vacation in years.

01:39.199 --> 01:41.470
And look what you did...
you brought the bad weather.

01:41.535 --> 01:45.174
So can we please just stop fighting
so we can get some sunshine?

01:45.239 --> 01:47.376
<i># Oh, I said #</i>

01:47.441 --> 01:49.678
<i># They don't cry #</i>

01:49.743 --> 01:52.681
<i>My mom, the quintessential happy housewife.</i>

01:52.746 --> 01:54.049
<i># Cry-yi-yi #</i>

01:54.114 --> 01:56.218
<i># My, oh, my #</i>

01:56.283 --> 01:59.521
<i>My dad, my hero and my role model.</i>

01:59.586 --> 02:00.587
<i>I wanted to be just like him.</i>

02:00.654 --> 02:02.357
<i># I wonder why #</i>

02:02.422 --> 02:06.028
- <i># Silly boy #</i>
- <i># Told my girl we had to break up #</i>

02:06.093 --> 02:08.197
<i># Silly boy #</i>

02:08.262 --> 02:10.699
<i>But that was before
our summer at Kellerman's.</i>

02:10.764 --> 02:14.234
<i>The summer I stopped being the baby for good.</i>

02:14.301 --> 02:17.612
<i># Big girls don't cry #</i>

02:33.253 --> 02:36.225
For seniors, we have water polo
in the middle pool.

02:36.290 --> 02:37.826
And for kiddies,

02:37.891 --> 02:41.597
popsicles... orange, lemon, lime...

02:41.662 --> 02:43.699
all in the main lodge.

02:43.764 --> 02:48.670
And at 1:30, boats are on the lake.
Learn to row, work those arms.

02:48.735 --> 02:53.108
And at 5:00, dinner is served.
We have meatloaf.

02:53.173 --> 02:57.312
Jake! The prodigal son has returned.

02:57.377 --> 02:59.481
