to do something so well.

20:50.249 --> 20:52.486
Your parents must be really proud of you.

20:52.551 --> 20:56.424
I don't know. We haven't spoken
in a few years, so...

20:56.489 --> 20:58.159
What's your name?

20:58.224 --> 20:59.927
- Frances.
- Thank you.

20:59.992 --> 21:02.029
But everyone calls me Baby.

21:02.094 --> 21:03.095
Does that bother you?

21:04.163 --> 21:06.834
No. Not really.

21:06.899 --> 21:09.203
