<i># What a lovely way to burn. #</i>

26:31.557 --> 26:33.560
- Johnny?
- Hey, kid.

26:33.626 --> 26:35.629
I need you to come with me.

26:35.694 --> 26:39.073
It's about Penny. Come on.

26:44.036 --> 26:45.538
Hey, what's going on?

26:47.239 --> 26:49.913
I'm in trouble, Johnny.

27:03.155 --> 27:04.634
How...

27:07.326 --> 27:10.297
- Whose is it?
- Doesn't matter.

27:10.362 --> 27:13.534
Yeah, it matters. Whoever he is
