<i># Just a little, just a little #</i>

33:10.155 --> 33:13.659
<i># Please love me #</i>

33:15.660 --> 33:21.568
<i># Sometimes I get a little troubled #</i>

33:21.633 --> 33:24.871
<i># Yeah, yeah #</i>

33:24.936 --> 33:27.908
<i># And I don't know #</i>

33:27.973 --> 33:31.682
