I have money for you.

34:23.562 --> 34:26.099
$250.

34:26.164 --> 34:28.301
It's all there.

34:28.366 --> 34:30.737
- You're kidding?
- Mm.

34:30.802 --> 34:32.706
We'll pay it back, Baby, every cent.

34:32.771 --> 34:34.908
No. We won't.

34:34.973 --> 34:36.376
You don't have to pay it back.

34:36.440 --> 34:38.011
That's even worse. We're not a charity case.

34:38.076 --> 34:41.014
Yes, we are, Johnny.

34:41.079 --> 34:44.251
It's not charity.

34:44.315 --> 34:47.254
I want to hire you.

34:47.319 --> 34:49.056
For dance lessons.

34:49.121 --> 34:50.998
For who?

34:54.326 --> 34:55.495
For me.

34:55.560 --> 34:58.031
Give me a break. That's way too much money.

34:58.096 --> 35:00.200
No, it isn't.

35:00.265 --> 35:03.769
I wanna dance
in the end of summer talent show.

35:03.835 --> 35:05.314
Why?

35:07.439 --> 35:11.678
Because it's good for the human
brain to learn new things.

35:11.743 --> 35:14.314
It keeps you from getting senile.

35:16.548 --> 35:18.285
Fine.

35:18.350 --> 35:20.687
But I don't take handouts.

35:20.752 --> 35:23.790
So I expect you to show up 9:00 a.m. sharp,

35:23.855 --> 35:26.460
in proper clothing,

35:26.525 --> 35:28.164
ready to work.

35:30.562 --> 35:32.371
I'll be there.

35:38.003 --> 35:40.807
<i># Please #</i>

35:40.872 --> 35:45.878
<i># Love me. #</i>

35:52.350 --> 35:54.821
- Okay, you ready?
- Mm.

35:54.886 --> 35:56.256
Six, seven, eight.

35:56.321 --> 35:59.392
One, <i>two</i>, three, four. <i>Two,</i> three, four.

35:59.457 --> 36:02.596
Two, three, four. Two, three, four.

36:02.661 --> 36:04.598
You don't step on the one.
You gotta start on the two.

36:04.663 --> 36:07.567
<i>Two,</i> three, four.
Find the <i>two,</i> you understand?

36:07.632 --> 36:09.603
- <i>Two,</i> three...
- No.

36:09.668 --> 36:10.977
Can you count?

36:12.304 --> 36:15.509
One, <i>two</i>, three, four. One, <i>two,</i> three, four.

36:15.574 --> 36:20.780
One, <i>two,</i> three, four. Find it.
Listen. Watch me.

36:21.513 --> 36:24.551
Six, seven, eight. One, <i>two,</i> three, four.

36:24.616 --> 36:26.286
<i>Two,</i> three, four.

36:26.351 --> 36:30.090
<i>Two,</i> three, four. <i>Two</i>, three, four.

