Two, three. Bigger steps.

36:39.497 --> 36:41.768
Both of your toes... Two, three, four.

36:41.833 --> 36:44.971
Soft, but it's locked, okay?
Two, three, four.

36:45.036 --> 36:48.074
Two, three... Head up.

36:48.139 --> 36:50.911
Relax. Breathe.

36:50.976 --> 36:54.181
Frame. Look, spaghetti arms.

36:54.246 --> 36:57.350
This is my dance space.
This is your dance space.

36:57.415 --> 36:59.753
I don't go into yours,
you don't go into mine.

36:59.818 --> 37:01.388
You gotta hold the frame.

37:01.453 --> 37:03.023
Again.

37:03.088 --> 37:05.825
Two, three, four.
Let your whole body feel it.

37:05.890 --> 37:07.660
It's not just your feet.

37:08.025 --> 37:09.895
What was that?

37:10.660 --> 37:13.700
I'm ready. I was preparing.

37:13.765 --> 37:16.803
Two, three, four. Use your hips.

37:16.868 --> 37:19.039
Two, three, four. Don't touch your hips,
just use them.

37:19.104 --> 37:22.342
Two, three, four. Two, three, four.

37:22.407 --> 37:24.578
- Two, three, four.
- There we go.

37:24.643 --> 37:26.079
Two, three, four.

37:30.782 --> 37:32.452
Feel your partner. Two, three, four.

37:32.517 --> 37:33.587
It's gotta be off of them.

37:33.652 --> 37:34.721
There's nobody there.

37:34.786 --> 37:36.856
You have to imagine there's somebody there,

37:36.921 --> 37:39.092
just like you have to imagine
you have more rhythm.

37:39.157 --> 37:42.495
Two, three, four. Two, three, four.

37:42.560 --> 37:43.663
Two, three, four.

37:51.436 --> 37:53.873
Look at my eyes. Hey.

37:53.938 --> 37:55.440
Not like that.

37:58.977 --> 38:01.355
- They're so large, I just...
- That's funny.

38:07.752 --> 38:09.823
There we go.

38:09.888 --> 38:11.060
Better. Two...

38:12.390 --> 38:15.132
Two, three, four. Two, three, four.

38:28.106 --> 38:31.177
You look like my patients
at the V.A. hospital.

38:31.242 --> 38:32.778
What war have you been fighting?

38:34.212 --> 38:37.751
Oh, I just went for a really long hike.

38:37.816 --> 38:40.754
- By yourself?
- With Neil?

38:40.819 --> 38:43.657
No. By myself.

