41:53.745 --> 41:55.815
You're a good teacher, Johnny.

41:55.880 --> 41:58.985
You can train anyone.

41:59.050 --> 42:00.520
Even her.

42:04.389 --> 42:06.062
I'm in if you're in.

42:11.930 --> 42:14.501
