Follow my lead.

42:14.566 --> 42:19.472
One, two, three, four,
five, six, seven, eight.

42:19.537 --> 42:20.974
One, two, three.

42:21.039 --> 42:22.709
Cross-body lead.

42:22.774 --> 42:24.711
