You ready?

47:09.393 --> 47:11.097
You good?

47:11.162 --> 47:12.505
Yeah.

47:15.566 --> 47:17.170
Whoo!

47:17.235 --> 47:19.038
All right, lifts are all about trust.

47:19.103 --> 47:22.414
