47:43.594 --> 47:44.595
Whichever one is here,

47:44.662 --> 47:47.533
'cause the next one, you know...

47:47.598 --> 47:49.268
is gonna be in the water.

47:49.333 --> 47:51.404
Okay.

47:52.669 --> 47:54.440
Okay.

47:54.505 --> 47:55.779
Come on!

47:57.275 --> 47:58.276
- You ready?
- I'm ready.

47:58.342 --> 48:00.546
Okay, here we go.

