50:28.726 --> 50:30.313
I...

50:31.149 --> 50:32.613
Marge.

50:43.474 --> 50:45.852
- You mind?
- Please.

50:51.982 --> 50:53.621
That looks good.

50:54.919 --> 50:57.092
You should have one.

50:58.556 --> 51:01.594
You look really fantastic, by the way.

51:01.659 --> 51:04.397
Your husband must feel like
he won the lottery.

51:05.262 --> 51:07.433
