51:25.416 --> 51:26.520
Well, it's just me.

51:28.819 --> 51:30.222
We're divorced.

51:30.287 --> 51:31.657
Oh, I'm so sorry.

51:31.722 --> 51:33.692
Oh, don't be. I'm having a ball.

51:33.757 --> 51:36.162
